<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Philadelphia</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Ζήνωνι χαίρειν Πύρων. 

    <lb n="2"/>καλῶς ποιήσεις, καθὰ καὶ 

    <lb n="3"/>προσεφώνησας ἀξιωθεὶς 

    <lb n="4"/>καὶ ὡμολόγησας πᾶν τὸ 

    <lb n="5"/>δυνατὸν ποιήσειν, φροντίσας 

    <lb n="6"/>ὅπως τό τε παιδίον ἱματισθῆι 

    <lb n="7"/>καὶ εἰς τὸ παλαιστρίδιον ἀπο-

    <lb n="8"/>στέλληται <g type="dipunct"/> μετὰ δὲ ταῦτα 

    <lb n="9"/>αὐτό γε τὸ ἀναγκαῖον περὶ 

    <lb n="10"/>σιταρίου φροντίσας, ὅπως μὴ 

    <lb n="11"/>ἐνδεεῖς ὦμεν καὶ ἐλαιδίου 

    <lb n="12"/>καὶ <choice><corr>ἄν</corr><sic>καν</sic></choice> τί σοι ἄλλο φαίνηται, ἵνα 

    <lb n="13"/>παυσώμεθα ἀσχημονοῦντες· 

    <lb n="14"/>καὶ εἴ σοι φαίνεται, μὴ <add place="supralinear">ἀποσύνταξον</add> ὥσπερ 

    <lb n="15"/>τοὺς κυβευτὰς ἐπιτηροῦντας 

    <lb n="16"/>ὡς ἂν εἰσερχώμεθα ἀπο-

    <lb n="17"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">παιδαριοῦν</unclear> γυμνοὺς ἱστάντας 

    <lb n="18"/>ἡμᾶς. ἀλλ᾽ εἴ σοι ἡμῶν 

    <lb n="19"/>πολυτελέστερον τὸ τριβώνιον 

    <lb n="20"/>φαίνεται εἶναι, ὀθόνιόν τι ἡμῖν 

    <lb n="21"/>σύνταξον δοῦναι, ἕως ἂν 

    <lb n="22"/>ἱματίου ἐπήβολοι γενώμεθα. 

    <lb n="23"/>καὶ τὸ ὅλον δὲ παῦσαι ἀσυνθετῶ<add place="supralinear">ν</add> 

    <lb n="24"/>περὶ ὧν ἂν ὁμολογήσηις ἡμῖν, 

    <lb n="25"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἵ</supplied>να μὴ <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἐ</supplied>ξαθυμῶμεν. καὶ πρὸς τὸν 

    <lb n="26"/>Ἰάσονα γράψον περὶ ὧν σοι φαίνεται. 

    <lb n="27"/>εὐτύχει. </ab></div><div n="meta.2101" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.2101" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="-275" notAfter="-226">Mitte III v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.2101" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Gehört zum Zenon - Archiv.</p></div><div n="meta.2101" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">PSI</title><biblScope type="volume">4</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">418</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">2101</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0238</series>; <biblScope type="volume">4</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">418</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0238;4;418" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.2101" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.2101" type="bibliography" subtype="translations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="de" default="NO"><head lang="de">Deutsch:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">Schubart, Ein Jahrtausend am Nil (1923) 33.</bibl></listBibl><listBibl lang="fr" default="NO"><head lang="de">Französisch:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">Orrieux, Les papyrus de Zenon (1983), S. 134</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.2101" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><placeName type="ancientFindspot" cert="high" full="yes">Philadelphia</placeName> (<geogName type="nome" cert="hi